26
00:01:34,863 --> 00:01:37,570
You have to buy her trust.

27
00:01:45,517 --> 00:01:46,635
Where do they sell it?

28
00:01:48,530 --> 00:01:49,210
How much does it cost?

29
00:01:50,388 --> 00:01:51,720
You sure are your dad’s boy.

30
00:01:51,821 --> 00:01:52,700
Let’s get in.

31
00:01:54,138 --> 00:01:56,138
