32
00:01:56,138 --> 00:01:57,223
Can you sell it to me?

33
00:01:58,084 --> 00:01:59,226
What are you talking about!?

34
00:01:59,226 --> 00:02:00,918
Trusts aren’t bought with money!

35
00:03:02,686 --> 00:03:04,686
