36
00:03:05,607 --> 00:03:06,537
This is my favorite.
(Haeb’s Salon)

37
00:03:07,168 --> 00:03:08,440
Pao, get those beans for me.

38
00:03:11,903 --> 00:03:13,625
What about mine, Auntie?

39
00:03:14,828 --> 00:03:15,598
Thank you.

40
00:03:16,684 --> 00:03:17,687
Thank you.

41
00:03:17,687 --> 00:03:19,019
This one’s rotten.

42
00:03:23,811 --> 00:03:25,000
Look at this, Bank.

43
00:03:27,706 --> 00:03:31,475
Can I ask you something very serious?

44
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:33,409
What is it?

45
00:03:34,799 --> 00:03:37,183
You like Lin, right?

46
00:03:46,734 --> 00:03:47,738
Bank.

47
00:03:47,839 --> 00:03:49,250
Tong’s not answering

48
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:50,974
that means he likes her.

49
00:03:51,378 --> 00:03:53,863
Hey, Uncle. I don’t like Lin.

50
00:03:55,498 --> 00:03:57,372
